snippet.title: Are Modi's James Bond Spying on Black Money Holders?

localized.description:
Are Modi's James Bond spying on black money holders? In the latest edition on Mann ki baat PM Narendra Modi said that PMO is getting dozens of phone calls about black money and income tax department and ED are raiding after these calls.
